Get residuals

residuals.RMASCA.Rd

This function returns the residual of the underlying linear mixed models

# S3 method for RMASCA
residuals(object, variable = NA)

Arguments

object

An RMASCA object
variable

The name of the variable(s) you want. NA returns all (default).

Value

A list of residuals per variable

Examples

load("PE.Rdata")
residuals(model, variable = c("IL-6", "PlGF"))
